_sText: With hundreds upon hundreds of lights, 60 spawn points, realistic sounds, and the Star Wars theme we all love, this map is a masterpiece for everyone to enjoy.  This map has been around 4 months in the making.  Attention to detail and devotion to quality have once again proven their value in this astounding end product.  For a video demonstration: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mUhgHYqr1wA
